&lt;p&gt;This role will build and lead Datadog’s new centralized pricing function, developing a clear, scalable approach to how we price and package our products. The Director will partner closely with Product, Finance, and GTM teams to design pricing models that make it easier for customers to buy, adopt, and grow with Datadog. This is a highly visible, high-impact role that will shape how Datadog captures value across its expanding platform and will own key monetization and operational responsibilities as the function scales.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
