&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive Datadog’s pricing and monetization vision to align customer value with company growth objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute strategies that make Datadog’s platform easier to buy, adopt, and expand across customer segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner across Product, Finance, and GTM teams to ensure pricing models reflect value delivered and support sustainable revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead data-driven pricing research and analytics to evaluate elasticity, usage behavior, and margin impact, guiding decisions that simplify offerings and improve predictability for customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and scale pricing governance that ensures consistency, transparency, and discipline across product lines and deal models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion a customer-first approach to pricing that reinforces trust, transparency, and long-term partnership.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven pricing and monetization leader with deep experience in high-growth SaaS or cloud platforms. (10+ years)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic and analytical operator who connects product telemetry, customer economics, and go-to-market execution with a strong understanding of usage-based and value-based business models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communicator who can clearly distill complex pricing concepts into clear narratives and can align cross-functional executives and internal teams around a unified pricing vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at connecting business strategy to pricing outcomes that drive adoption, expansion, and retention, using data and insights to inform complex tradeoffs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
